The unique nature and recreational area 'Westeinderplassen' is perhaps Aalsmeer's biggest asset. With Westeinderstrand and the promenade, Aalsmeer offers the comfort and benefits of living in a village, with all urban amenities within reach. This makes Aalsmeer a pleasant place to live, right in the Randstad. For water lovers, this is the ideal place.

Aalsmeer has a rich community life and a varied shopping offer. For larger shopping centers, you can go to Amstelveen and Hoofddorp, both easily accessible by bike or public transport.

