- A recently laid out and well-maintained garden with an irrigation system;
- More than 475 m² of living space;
- Unique: connection between the carriage house and farmhouse, making it one large usable living space;
- 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, 4 toilets, front room, formal sitting room, eat-in kitchen, 2 offices/workspaces, gym, garage, horse stables.

