Description 
Living in this beautiful semi-detached villa is truly a pleasure. Situated on a 683 m² plot and just a stone’s throw from the nature and walking area “Het Naaldenveld,” this home offers an oasis of peace and space. The property is well-maintained and forms a fantastic foundation for a wonderful family home. With no fewer than 7 bedrooms, the house offers plenty of room for the whole family. Whether you need extra rooms for work, hobbies, or guests, the space is there. The living and dining rooms are spacious and filled with natural light thanks to the many windows. The double garage, approximately 34 m², provides ample space for your cars, bicycles, and extra storage. Additionally, the house itself offers plenty of storage options, including space under the roof, the basement (with standing height), and the attic, which has a height of 2.70 meters at its peak. The large garden offers both sunny and shaded spots throughout the day and is an ideal place for gardening, relaxing, or for children to play. In short, a fantastic home for family gatherings.

Location 
The house is located in a child-friendly neighborhood in Aerdenhout, where many young families reside. The area is known for its quiet, green surroundings and offers plenty of options for families. Just a short bike ride away, on Zandvoortselaan in Heemstede, there are high-quality shops providing a wide range of daily groceries. Aerdenhout offers excellent primary education, while nearby cities like Haarlem and Heemstede provide numerous options for secondary education. The area also boasts a wealth of sports facilities and natural areas, such as forests, dunes, and beaches. The Heemstede-Aerdenhout train station is less than a 10-minute bike ride away, offering direct connections to Haarlem/Amsterdam and The Hague/Rotterdam. Amsterdam, Schiphol, and The Hague are just 30 minutes away by car, making it an ideal location for families working in the Randstad region.

Layout 
Ground floor: Entrance, vestibule with meter cupboard and glass partition, spacious hall and corridor with a toilet with a fountain, storage closet, and access to the basement (17 m²) with standing height, where the central heating system is located, and space for a second refrigerator. Bright living room with fireplace, built-in wardrobe, parquet flooring, and French doors to the garden, leading into the adjacent dining room. Spacious closed kitchen with various built-in appliances and connections for a washing machine and dryer. The kitchen provides access to the garden. Office/bedroom with French doors to the garden, adjacent to a bathroom with a shower and washbasin.

First floor: Landing, toilet with a fountain, access to 3 spacious bedrooms, all with built-in wardrobes. The bedrooms at the front offer access to the south-facing balcony. Bathroom with shower, toilet, and double sink.

Second floor: Landing with access to a shower room, loft ladder to the large attic. 3 bedrooms with washbasins, built-in wardrobes and/or storage space, and plenty of natural light through the many windows.

Special features
For layout and dimensions, please refer to the floor plan;
Living area approx. 209 m², gross volume approx. 896 m³ (according to NEN 2580);
Plot size 683 m²;
Built in 1933;
Partially equipped with double glazing;
Heating through central heating boiler (Nefit 2020) and hot water through 2 electric boilers;
9 rooms, including 7 bedrooms;
Double garage of approx. 34 m²;
Parking on private property;
Notary chosen by the seller;
Transfer and delivery in consultation.

Deze karakteristieke en riante vrijstaande villa met aangebouwde garage is gelegen op een zonnige kavel. 
De villa is met hoogwaardige materialen stijlvol uit- en opgebouwd waardoor er een fantastische leefruimte is gerealiseerd. Door de royale maatvoering en de zeer goede indeling is deze comfortabele villa uitstekend geschikt als familiehuis.

Via een elektrisch hekwerk aan de voorzijde bereikt men de grote oprijlaan met parkeerruimte voor meer auto’s. Door de zuid ligging is er in het huis een fijne lichtinval en is de rondom de villa gelegen tuin zeer zonnig. De boompartijen en de mooie heesters zorgen zowel in het huis als in de tuin voor optimale privacy. Een gezellige veranda met leuk zicht over de zonnige tuin een berging, moestuin en een kas completeren het geheel.

Dit fijne familiehuis is gelegen in het breedste gedeelte van de laan tegenover een plantsoen. Goede centrale ligging op 5 minuten fietsafstand van NS-station Heemstede-Aerdenhout. Schiphol, Den Haag en Amsterdam zijn binnen 30 minuten met de auto bereikbaar. Winkels, uitstekende scholen, kinderdagverblijven en sportfaciliteiten zoals de hockeyclub Rood-Wit, voetbalclub Koninklijke HFC en de Kennemer Golf Club bevinden zich in de directe nabijheid. Het gezellige centrum van Heemstede en het historische stadscentrum van Haarlem met zijn ruime aanbod op cultureel en culinair gebied en zijn uitgebreide winkelaanbod liggen op fietsafstand! De ligging tussen natuurgebieden en op korte afstand van het strand maakt het plaatje compleet.

