WATER-SIDED AND ENERGY-EFFICIENT SEMI-DETACHED HOUSE WITH 15 SOLAR PANELS AND ENERGY LABEL A+!

Are you looking for a spacious, modern and energy-efficient home? Then this is exactly what you are looking for! With a living area of ??154 m², an energy label A+, 15 solar panels and a beautiful location on the water, this ready-to-move-in home from 2013 offers everything you need for comfortable living.

Upon arrival, you will immediately notice the private driveway with space for two cars, with an adjoining spacious storage room, which previously served as a garage. Entering the spacious hall, you will find the meter cupboard and a modern separate toilet with washbasin on the right. From the hall you walk through to the bright and spacious living room with air conditioning, which is extra spacious because part of the former garage has been incorporated into the living space. This means there is plenty of room for a cozy sitting area and a large dining table. The luxurious open kitchen in L-shape is a real eye-catcher and fully equipped. With a high-quality composite kitchen top, a separate bar and top appliances from Siemens and Miele, such as a combination microwave, oven, fridge-freezer, 5-burner induction hob, extractor hood, dishwasher and a hot water tap, this kitchen is a dream for every cooking enthusiast.

Through the patio doors in the living room you reach the beautifully landscaped backyard on the water. Here you can enjoy the outdoors in peace, with enough space for a lounge set and a dining table. The garden is also equipped with sun blinds, so that you can sit outside comfortably on warm days.

On the first floor there are three spacious bedrooms. Two rooms are located at the rear, one of which is currently used as a walk-in closet, but it can easily be converted into an extra bedroom or study. The large bedroom at the rear also has air conditioning. At the front you will find the third spacious bedroom and the modern bathroom, which is equipped with a walk-in shower, a washbasin unit with mirror wall and a second toilet.

