For daily shopping and other facilities, you can go to Oudorp or the De Mare shopping centre, which is a short distance away. Here you will find various supermarkets, shops, restaurants and sports facilities. Schools, childcare and medical facilities can also be found nearby. The district is conveniently located in relation to arterial roads, so you can be on the A9 within a few minutes and easily travel to Amsterdam, Haarlem or other cities. In addition, there is a good public transport connection, with several bus stops within walking distance and the Alkmaar-Noord station in the vicinity.

Special features:
